# PS-2: Risk Communication
VERSION: 1.0.0
PRIORITY: SYSTEM
SCOPE: Any risky design decision or delivery delay

## CATEGORY CONTEXT
- Stakeholder Communication: Any report, meeting, or update intended for stakeholders.

ENFORCE: All significant risks must be communicated to relevant stakeholders in business language with mitigation options.
PROHIBIT: Omitting or downplaying risks; withholding risk information.
ON VIOLATION: Escalate to Product Governance Skill → notify orchestrator.
